      <title>2024 年德国经济萎缩，公司破产数量激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/german-company-insolvencies-jumped-in-2024-as-economy-shrank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于德国企业不堪经济萎缩的压力，2024 年德国企业破产率跃升近 17%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/german-company-insolvencies-jumped-in-2024-as-economy-shrank</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 09:31:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
